          <title>
            <string language="en">The Nature of Protest</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Die Natur des Protestes</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">La nature de la protestation</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">A natureza do protesto</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Natura della protesta</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Η φύση της διαμαρτυρίας</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">La naturaleza de la protesta</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">This lesson will focus on the nature of protest by examining the different avenues that people take to express their opinions. </string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Humanities</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Social Sciences</string>
          </keyword>
          <coverage>
            <string language="en">North America</string>
          </coverage>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Diese Lektion konzentriert auf die Natur des 
Protestes, indem sie die unterschiedlichen Alleen überprüft, denen 
Leute nehmen, um ihre Meinungen auszudrücken.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Cette leçon se concentrera sur la nature de la 
protestation en examinant les différentes avenues que les gens 
prennent pour exprimer leurs avis.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Esta lição focalizará na natureza do protesto 
examinando as avenidas diferentes que os povos fazem exame para 
expressar suas opiniões.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Questa lezione metterà a fuoco sulla natura della
protesta esaminando i viali differenti che la gente prende per 
esprimere i loro pareri.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Αυτό το μάθημα θα εστιάσει στη φύση της διαμαρτυρίας 
με την εξέταση των διαφορετικών λεωφόρων που οι άνθρωποι παίρνουν
για να εκφράσουν τις απόψεις τους.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Esta lección se centrará en la naturaleza de la 
protesta examinando las diversas avenidas que la gente toma para 
expresar sus opiniones.</string>
          </description>
